snippet.title: EXP: War Trauma - Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description: EXP: War Trauma is a psychological horror game that follows a WW2 solidier, and Cortez Productions revealed some terrifying gameplay during the Future Games Show at Gamescom 2022. EXP: War Trauma is coming soon, with a demo available on Steam right now.
